{"tid":1464393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[代發] 機場集會","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:50.000Z","uid":304013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e20753fc6cfb0b16c591d1784a979501da547dd","tid":1464393,"uid":304013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"來自我嘅一個朋友<br />\n<br />\n其實我好理解遊行示威活動，亦支持呢d，但喺機場集會原意喺癱瘓航班同提高國際關注，但喺近排開始演變成一個不合作活動，去圍人地，唔人走，直接嚴重影響到市民同遊客，更加令更多人反感，呢個根本唔喺原意<br />\n<br />\n我希望你哋明白取消航班喺件無咩所謂嘅事嘅，因為至少有賠償，但喺航班繼續而你哋唔比入就好大件事，喺完全無賠償，你可能覺得我自私，但喺真喺好希望你可以代市民同遊客嘅角度諗"},{"pid":"ca6b5081671d61d3017789bfd40b24a1e5b6b813","tid":1464393,"uid":304013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ede385034ffd40d4426f93586d6eb55f3edc5b2","tid":1464393,"uid":304013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b7936c4dbd6aa710899c75d663c1d567300451","tid":1464393,"uid":304013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec4c80a19da4361c795621dc4c9fb6b121b8471","tid":1464393,"uid":304013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g